description: A collaborative tool for creating images with AI.
title: Artbreeder
introduction: Artbreeder is a platform that allows users to create characters, artworks, and more using multiple AI-powered tools. With 10 million users and access to 250 million images, users can unleash their creativity like never before.
features: Composer: Create by mixing images and text together.
Collager: Create an image out of simple shapes, image, and text.
